        <h1>Create Custom {{ category_name }} Workouts for Apple Watch</h1>
        <p class="workout-category-description">
            This guide helps you create custom {{ category_name_lower }} workouts that you can use with the Workouts app on your Apple Watch. 
            Create {{ category_workout_types }} {{ category_name_lower }} workouts on your iPhone and send them to your Apple Watch.</p>

        <div class="workout-separator"></div>

        <div class="install-instructions">
            <h2>Download Workout Builder for iPhone</h2>
            <p>1. Download <a href="../index.html">Workout Builder for iPhone</a> for free.</p>
            <p>2. Either create a custom workout or use one of our pre-built workouts</p>

            <h3>Create custom workouts</h3>
            <p>1. Create a custom workout by tapping the '+' button</p>
            <p>2. Enter your workout details and tap 'Done'</p>
            <p>3. Tap 'Send to Apple Watch' to send the workout to your paired Apple Watch</p>
            <p>4. In the Workouts app on your Apple Watch, choose the workout you created</p>

